descriptionHtml:

With this viral app, YOU control the beats of some of the most famous and very juicy songs on TikTok.

Every trending song is split up into several samples and beats. Then you are the DJ recreating the songs and beats as you remember them. Put on your favorite headphones and start the juicy beats!

GUIDED MODE:
If you don't remember the song there's also a guided mode where you will be hinted the next button to press.

SOCIAL:
Try to upload a video of your own jam!
It would also be perfect for a duet...

Many have gone viral before with a video of this juicy app - you might be next!

Find other videos of this app on TikTok by searching for "TikSongs". (the iOS version)
